#################################################
##### Dependencies:
#################################################


	<Try with pip or pip3>

1): pip install flask
2): pip install Flask-RESTful
3): pip install flask flask-cors


################################################
##### How to run
################################################

1): Initialize the database: --> (this will create the database and insert some dummy data....)
	
	Run in terminal > python init_db.py

2): Run the app and start interacting with API.
	
	Run in terminal > python app_2_best.py
	
	
	Working:
	========
	
	> Copy & Paste the following line in your browser: ==> http://127.0.0.1:5000/
		The output should be: ==> All Ok!
	
	> Read data using URL:
		> http://127.0.0.1:5000/polygons
	
	> Read specific polygon from URL:
		> http://127.0.0.1:5000/polygons/1
	
	> Insert, Edit, Or delete polygon data using URL: 
		> if method=="PUT"    ==> the record will be updated
		> if method=="GET"    ==> get the specific polygon
		> if method=="DELETE" ==> delete the specific polygon.

